pipeline_summary.name: Daily Sales Report
pipeline_summary.description: Sequential linear pipeline that generates daily sales reports by querying PostgreSQL, converting to CSV, creating a PDF chart, and emailing the report.

components.name: Query Sales Data
components.description: Extracts daily aggregated sales data from the PostgreSQL sales table using a dateparameterized SQL query.
outputs: query result set (aggregated sales by date and product)

upstream_policy.description: First step in linear pipeline, no upstream dependencies.

components.name: Transform Sales Data to CSV
components.description: Converts the extracted sales result set into a CSV file using pandas and stores it on the local filesystem.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful execution of query_sales_data.

components.name: Generate PDF Chart
components.description: Creates a barchart PDF visualizing sales by product using matplotlib, reading the CSV data and writing the chart to a temporary file.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful execution of transform_to_csv.

components.name: Email Sales Report
components.description: Emails the daily sales report to management, attaching the CSV and PDF files generated in previous steps.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful generation of the PDF chart.

connections.purpose: SMTP server for sending report emails

description.default: Sequential linear pipeline that generates daily sales reports by querying PostgreSQL, converting to CSV, creating a PDF chart, and emailing the report.

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

to.description: Recipient email address for the sales report

files.description: List of file paths to attach to the email

sources: PostgreSQL sales table filtered by execution date ({{ ds }})
sinks: Email delivery of daily sales report to management@company.com
